solidbase.util
Class Tokenizer

java.lang.Object
  solidbase.util.Tokenizer

public class Tokenizer
extends Object

This is a tokenizer for a language like SQL. It maintains the current line number, it is case insensitive, and it ignores whitespace.

Author:
René M. de Bloois
